message.content:
To complete the task of unpacking the suitcase, you need to follow these steps:

1. GotoLocation(sofa.n.01_1) - Go to the sofa where the objects should be placed.
2. PickupObject(sock.n.01_1) - Pick up the first sock from the carton.
3. PutObject(sock.n.01_1) - Put the first sock on the sofa.
4. PickupObject(sock.n.01_2) - Pick up the second sock from the carton.
5. PutObject(sock.n.01_2) - Put the second sock on the sofa.
6. PickupObject(bottle__of__perfume.n.01_1) - Pick up the bottle of perfume from the carton.
7. PutObject(bottle__of__perfume.n.01_1) - Put the bottle of perfume on the sofa.
8. PickupObject(toothbrush.n.01_1) - Pick up the toothbrush from the carton.
9. PutObject(toothbrush.n.01_1) - Put the toothbrush on the sofa.
10. PickupObject(notebook.n.01_1) - Pick up the notebook from the carton.
11. PutObject(notebook.n.01_1) - Put the notebook on the sofa.

Once you have completed all these steps, the suitcase will be unpacked and the objects will be placed on the sofa.
